title: Christmas Video
description:
This video was finished on 12/15/08. It was our first project, and was create all by one person, which probably explains it's poor quality. It took a few months to create, and animating took nearly as long. We had a slow computer at the time, and with it being HD some frames were taking eight minutes!
We should mention that Playmobil (R) does not endorse this video, or probably even know it exists.
This project was created entirely with Free Open-Source software, and you are free to distribute it in any way you'd like.
